stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> idle

    idle --> gate: /start or message
    gate --> idle: unauthorized (silent)
    gate --> idle: on cooldown
    gate --> discovery: authorized

    discovery --> discovery: collecting info
    discovery --> matching: profile complete
    discovery --> idle: no opportunities

    matching --> negotiation: opportunity selected

    negotiation --> negotiation: modifying terms
    negotiation --> review: submit for review

    review --> review: collecting reviewer feedback
    review --> negotiation: counter-offer (round 2)
    review --> resolution: decision made

    resolution --> idle: approved → Beta App
    resolution --> idle: rejected → cooldown (3 days)
